        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued July 26 at 7:26PM MDT until July 26 at 8:00PM MDT by NWS Great Falls MT</headline>
        <description>At 725 PM MDT, a severe thunderstorm was located near Turner, or 33
miles west of Whitewater, moving southeast at 20 mph.

HAZARD...Ping pong ball size hail and 60 mph wind gusts.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...People and animals outdoors will be injured. Expect hail
damage to roofs, siding, windows, and vehicles. Expect wind
damage to roofs, siding, and trees.

Locations impacted include...
Turner.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.</instruction>
